title: Aivoryy
info:
Norwegian lyrics:
"Vi kan'ke kode eller lage musikk,
grafikken blir jo rævva,
men det driter vi i for vi er Ivory. Åå-å-åååh for vi er Ivory! Hei!

Vi kan'ke kode eller lage musikk,
grafikken blir jo rævva,
men det driter vi i for vi er Ivory. Åå-å-åååh for vi er Ivory! Hei!

*Sniff sniff* Her lukter det...
*Sniff sniff* Ivory!"

English:
"We can't code or create music,
graphics are fucked up,
but we don't care because we are Ivory! Oh-o-ooh because we are Ivory! Hi!

We can't code or create music,
graphics are fucked up,
but we don't care because we are Ivory! Oh-o-ooh because we are Ivory! Hi!

*sniff sniff* It's smelly here...
*sniff sniff* Ivory!"
